{"tid":2152680,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港01：鄭松泰決定延任：泛民若不接受　應反思未來都不參選","createTime":"2020-08-12T06:31:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-13T10:12:59.000Z","uid":271829,"like":25,"dislike":219,"uniUserReply":112,"replies":[{"pid":"d70a002d90d962769c4817a5f90bd57d58de7efe","tid":2152680,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T06:31:15.000Z","msg":"全國人大常委會昨日決定現屆立法會延任不少於一年，20多名民主派議員昨發明質疑決定違反《基本法》第69條，但未定留任抑或「總辭」。<br />\n<br />\n未有參與聯署的熱血公民立法會議員鄭松泰今天（12日）表示，會延任一年，他指若民主派決定不延任，應反思未來都不參加選舉。民主派昨午開會商討去留問題，會上未有結論。<br />\n<br />\n鄭松泰接受傳媒訪問時表示，「如果民主派討論後有一個方向，一齊不參與（延任），我覺得立場應該清晰，不要參與的不是這次的委任，不要參與的應該是香港的選舉制度。」<br />\n<br />\n民主黨議員涂謹申昨日表示，泛民將共同商討，但認為泛民若然總辭，立法會將沒有反對聲音，可做更多壞事，「暫時聽到希望全部留低的人，反對派議員全部留低聲音多少少」。「抗爭派」張可森質疑，國安處日前拘捕黎智英等人「拉人封艇」，反問若泛民留任，「係咪要入去配合暴政做政治花瓶？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/5012611/org/e6d2de4a3a6a04cbc9ab24ada680e811.jpg/dJWKPtC91Luvd7_1Jg9gkiR2XZnn14Ml6EWsl-hFrJc?v=w1120\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F5012611%2Forg%2Fe6d2de4a3a6a04cbc9ab24ada680e811.jpg%2FdJWKPtC91Luvd7_1Jg9gkiR2XZnn14Ml6EWsl-hFrJc%3Fv%3Dw1120&h=29ee1071&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n民主派近日開會商討對策，當中將會列舉不同可能性，從而定出同應對方案。（張浩維攝／資料圖片）"},{"pid":"cc9025616fcbde3af4015717dfc4f56b28d682ce","tid":2152680,"uid":362865,"like":101,"dislike":2,"score":99,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T06:32:05.000Z","msg":"有01認證, 你仲有咩講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab721e51f838b53b8478a1578b662d07d28da110","tid":2152680,"uid":137725,"like":96,"dislike":1,"score":95,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T06:32:43.000Z","msg":"虫太有老婆有仔女要養<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />乖乖聽話了"},{"pid":"ec197e51ce06eac57787bdc3d71edce10eacff08","tid":2152680,"uid":295230,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T06:33:19.000Z","msg":"熱狗必勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f1e0287e6de4e394ae06c4272cc0a3dc9315a13","tid":2152680,"uid":29381,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T06:34:22.000Z","msg":"張可森係咪串緊蟲泰係政治花瓶 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35923a475328ff57586ac1988576c86f7867df19","tid":2152680,"uid":165361,"like":43,"dislike":1,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T06:34:32.000Z","msg":"人地要反思,自己就唔洗"},{"pid":"c2a8ae1279f3c2f55e38f02c70257b9d9db290f3","tid":2152680,"uid":3482,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T06:34:42.000Z","msg":"咁講同建制果 d 撚人有咩分別 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31f5da94aef7160f6c634558bc195d8eff0e9d20","tid":2152680,"uid":28485,"like":63,"dislike":2,"score":61,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T06:35:17.000Z","msg":"點解佢咁撚黑人憎"},{"pid":"415c46f3fba4f21cf75ede4971a288377e801c34","tid":2152680,"uid":4151,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T06:36:04.000Z","msg":"熱血建制😂"},{"pid":"4e520171433949ee2d6b82d78e5cf59a40f729db","tid":2152680,"uid":295735,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T06:36:36.000Z","msg":"又係熱狗。。"},{"pid":"596de0ac01166dac0383e0a37068415ef5c7d4b3","tid":2152680,"uid":35604,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"31f5da94aef7160f6c634558bc195d8eff0e9d20","tid":2152680,"uid":28485,"like":63,"dislike":2,"score":61,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T06:35:17.000Z","msg":"點解佢咁撚黑人憎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T06:36:47.000Z","msg":"表忠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44110482c17e33553aa74babf7aa89f29f865818","tid":2152680,"uid":229225,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"d70a002d90d962769c4817a5f90bd57d58de7efe","tid":2152680,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T06:31:15.000Z","msg":"全國人大常委會昨日決定現屆立法會延任不少於一年，20多名民主派議員昨發明質疑決定違反《基本法》第69條，但未定留任抑或「